0.body: This is a demo book, only used for the sole pupose of working on the custom theme of the book.
0.title: Introduction

1.body: This book uses MdBook just like the main book. Prerequisites Rust Cargo MdBook (can be installed by cargo install mdbook) After setting everything up, it's as simple as Opening the folder in any IDE of choice Running the local mdbook server to see changes live. mdbook serve is the command to do that, make sure that your CWD is the folder the book is located in. Start improving the theme!

There are upto 9 elements which are considered as "endpoint" elements They are the 9 methods: get head post put delete connect options trace patch <get>/some/endpoint</get>\

<connect>/some/endpoint</connect>\
<options>/some/endpoint</options>\
